[div class=p 
	"In Ninja Storm, you select one of three teams of Power Rangers to battle through 5 areas, squaring off against Lothor's forces. These teams are the Wind Rangers (Red/Blue/Yellow), the Thunder Rangers (Crimson/Navy), and Samurai Ranger (Singular. The Green Samurai Ranger goes alone.). Each team has special abilities to help progress through the game, such as charging attacks as the Thunder Rangers, preforming feats of mobility as the Wind Rangers, and engaging an HP-draining super mode as the Samurai Ranger. At the end of each area is a boss which you fight as the rangers, then, upon defeat, fight again in a giant robot, the Megazord. These are essentially western duels where reflexes are everything, as you continually input correct combinations of directions and buttons before the boss does. Additionally, power discs can be found within areas to be used in Megazord fights.
	$LF
]div
