[ul 
	[li 
		"No major programming errors or glitches were used. However, I did play around with narrowly avoiding hurtboxes from enemies and hazards. I may have also abused the way certain enemies spawn (of which spawn from a different location depending on which way you face on the frame before they spawn), although I believe this behavior was as intentional as it was exploitable.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"No deaths were used to gain time. In fact, no hits were taken either.
		$LF
