[div class=p 
	"Picture this: You are an evil overlord named Lothor, who decided to take revenge against your brother by conquering the world. You have cannon fodder in countless amounts, and in increasing power. You also have some of the most formidable henchmen at your fingertips. Now imagine spending months to set up strategic planning, only to have it all crumbling down. Not by a team of bravehearted warriors, but three teens who were late to academic ninja training because they were too busy speedrunning The Ninja Warriors Again and Wild Gunman. The nightmare only gets worse... these losers are apparently cracked up on Mountain Dew and appear to move in a twitchy manner not-unlike these "speedrunner" people. And this guy in yellow, my goodness!!! He's so popped up, he thinks the torso is the superior method of human locomotion. And it's working!? These freakish creatures somehow became chosen to be next in line in a lineage your fellow evil-bookclub partners had spread horror stories about. And now, they had ruined everything, and in 26 minutes, too. Time to get a new hobby...
	$LF
